  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Don't Destroy On Load\" — A tale of memories engraved upon the board.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/97a97956c804778c15e2279f414590f1.poster.avif?t=1773759765\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/97a97956c804778c15e2279f414590f1.webm?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/97a97956c804778c15e2279f414590f1.mp4?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DDOL is a next-generation strategy game that fuses the tactical depth of card games with the overwhelming sense of dominance found in area-control board games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Succession of Souls and Board Dominance</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The board is more than just a grid; it is where \"Souls\" reside. Each turn, players drop a single card and pay the <strong>Soul Cost</strong> to pass their power down the line.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/475793d34106ffb2e57bbb39ed8a58ba.poster.avif?t=1773759765\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/475793d34106ffb2e57bbb39ed8a58ba.webm?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/475793d34106ffb2e57bbb39ed8a58ba.mp4?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Expansion,\" \"Reinforcement,\" \"Destruction\"... How will you manage your 15-card deck? Where will you channel your limited Souls? Every choice is engraved upon the board as a permanent legacy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ \"Lock\" – Severing the Chain of Succession</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the flow of souls is severed, a rejection manifests on the board in the form of heavy chains. This is the <strong>\"Lock\"</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The core of DDOL lies in this system: physically obstructing your opponent’s options and seizing control of their thoughts. A tense psychological battle over the only two \"Breakthrough\" cards allowed to each player. When the board is draped in golden chains and all paths are sealed, a rock-solid <strong>\"Checkmate\"</strong> is achieved.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/1bd31f183b9f8e92e6cafc56a3cd5fad.poster.avif?t=1773759765\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/1bd31f183b9f8e92e6cafc56a3cd5fad.webm?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/1bd31f183b9f8e92e6cafc56a3cd5fad.mp4?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>...That moment of catharsis, when your dominance is \"Finalized,\" is the true essence of DDOL.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/8cc4ec3570656b83f2f7e57781861c2b.poster.avif?t=1773759765\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/8cc4ec3570656b83f2f7e57781861c2b.webm?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/8cc4ec3570656b83f2f7e57781861c2b.mp4?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ \"Judge\" – Finalizing Your Dominance</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>\"Judge\"</strong> is more than just a results screen. It is a \"rite of passage\" granted only to those who have truly mastered the board and seized control.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, area size isn't the only thing that matters. Trap your opponent as planned, seal them with chains, and deliver the killing blow with your score.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The moment the golden chains lock the board and your dominance is \"Finalized\"—that pure catharsis is the true essence of DDOL.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Agile and Adorable – Unity-chan in Action!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Behind the deep strategic depth, a 3D Unity-chan moves dynamically across the board! The snappy tempo, synced with card actions, is one of the true highlights of this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the contrast between the intense tension of tactical planning and her charming, lively animations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/8207739f34390fd2630208c225378cec.poster.avif?t=1773759765\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/8207739f34390fd2630208c225378cec.webm?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/8207739f34390fd2630208c225378cec.mp4?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Don't Destroy On Load\" — A tale of memories engraved upon the board.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/97a97956c804778c15e2279f414590f1.poster.avif?t=1773759765\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/97a97956c804778c15e2279f414590f1.webm?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/97a97956c804778c15e2279f414590f1.mp4?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DDOL is a next-generation strategy game that fuses the tactical depth of card games with the overwhelming sense of dominance found in area-control board games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Succession of Souls and Board Dominance</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The board is more than just a grid; it is where \"Souls\" reside. Each turn, players drop a single card and pay the <strong>Soul Cost</strong> to pass their power down the line.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/475793d34106ffb2e57bbb39ed8a58ba.poster.avif?t=1773759765\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/475793d34106ffb2e57bbb39ed8a58ba.webm?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/475793d34106ffb2e57bbb39ed8a58ba.mp4?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Expansion,\" \"Reinforcement,\" \"Destruction\"... How will you manage your 15-card deck? Where will you channel your limited Souls? Every choice is engraved upon the board as a permanent legacy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ \"Lock\" – Severing the Chain of Succession</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the flow of souls is severed, a rejection manifests on the board in the form of heavy chains. This is the <strong>\"Lock\"</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The core of DDOL lies in this system: physically obstructing your opponent’s options and seizing control of their thoughts. A tense psychological battle over the only two \"Breakthrough\" cards allowed to each player. When the board is draped in golden chains and all paths are sealed, a rock-solid <strong>\"Checkmate\"</strong> is achieved.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/1bd31f183b9f8e92e6cafc56a3cd5fad.poster.avif?t=1773759765\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/1bd31f183b9f8e92e6cafc56a3cd5fad.webm?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/1bd31f183b9f8e92e6cafc56a3cd5fad.mp4?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>...That moment of catharsis, when your dominance is \"Finalized,\" is the true essence of DDOL.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/8cc4ec3570656b83f2f7e57781861c2b.poster.avif?t=1773759765\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/8cc4ec3570656b83f2f7e57781861c2b.webm?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/8cc4ec3570656b83f2f7e57781861c2b.mp4?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ \"Judge\" – Finalizing Your Dominance</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>\"Judge\"</strong> is more than just a results screen. It is a \"rite of passage\" granted only to those who have truly mastered the board and seized control.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, area size isn't the only thing that matters. Trap your opponent as planned, seal them with chains, and deliver the killing blow with your score.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The moment the golden chains lock the board and your dominance is \"Finalized\"—that pure catharsis is the true essence of DDOL.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Agile and Adorable – Unity-chan in Action!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Behind the deep strategic depth, a 3D Unity-chan moves dynamically across the board! The snappy tempo, synced with card actions, is one of the true highlights of this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the contrast between the intense tension of tactical planning and her charming, lively animations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/8207739f34390fd2630208c225378cec.poster.avif?t=1773759765\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/8207739f34390fd2630208c225378cec.webm?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4288300/extras/8207739f34390fd2630208c225378cec.mp4?t=1773759765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
